	quest.49F4016F012BFA95.quest_desc: ["&4&oRadical Red&r is a ROM Hack for Pokemon Red, it follows the same story as Pokemon Red... just much harder. \\\\n\\\\nYeah, this won't be easy. \\\\n\\\\nYou can start the &4&oSeries&r by Trading with a &4Trainer Associate&r to give him your &4Trader Card&r so you can start &4&oRadical Red&r."]
	quest.49F4016F012BFA95.title: "&4&oRadical Red"
	quest.4FD9219B6005D90E.quest_desc: ["Once you've beat &4&oRadical Red&r you can find &6Trainer Red&r the main character of the earliest games and media! \\n\\nHe is an optional fighter. This means he doesn't have a Signature Item, instead you'll need to find him wandering around in a certain Biome. That being any that can have End Cities. \\n\\nAll the years of fighting Trainers throughout multiple games and media made him a pretty good fighter, so bring your best! \\n\\nIf you can beat him you'll become the Kanto Legend!"]
	quest.4FD9219B6005D90E.title: "&6Trainer Red"
