	quest.5C335DBA0A7C23B5.title: "&3Elite Four Lance"
	quest.5D635B2021C98D41.quest_desc: ["If you want to fight the &3Elite Four&r and &5Champion&r you'll need to make your way to the Kanto League Gym! \\n\\nThis is a giant tower found in &d&lThe End&r. It is made of Purpur, End Stone, and has a giant Orange Pokeball in the front. \\n\\nThe first floor has a few Pokemart Traders, Nurses, and Loot you can take. The next few floors have each of the &3Elite Four&r. The highest floor having the &5Champion&r!"]
